{"tid":1997605,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真心想討論] 本土嘢點解好似好難吸引人","createTime":"2020-05-01T18:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T04:15:14.000Z","uid":277977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f16f007c109a0b184a0cba970728726c8af4562a","tid":1997605,"uid":277977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:57:13.000Z","msg":"其實香港一直都有引入外地文化，點解今時今日本土嘢咁難做主流(或起碼有返啲影響力)? <br />\n<br />\n有人為錢合拍、迎合內地市場呢個原因我明，但依加都有啲人想做本地市場e.g. viutv、本土電影 點解好似都係做唔起&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定時間問題?<br />\n(btw viutv黑市都幾jeng <br />\n<br />\n竟然點嘅本土作品先吸引到??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他國家好似自己做自己就有人行埋去 (曾經嘅香港pop cult都同日本有得fight ，點解日本keep到，香港keep唔到?<br />\n<br />\n想聽你地點諗"},{"pid":"94f5450c7f7da23e055cf6ebe6971f5701bbb64d","tid":1997605,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:59:50.000Z","msg":"市場細"},{"pid":"6243de322a355963c93921e17f0159a48cdec352","tid":1997605,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:06:02.000Z","msg":"拍得戲嘅導演好多都走哂去支那賺人仔<br />\n<br />\n香港唱片公司又唔肯培育多啲唔同類型嘅新人<br />\n當然好大因素都係香港人唔知幾時開始對於本土野一黎就踩左先，以搵個作品嘅缺點為樂，邊有人敢dam錢搞製作"},{"pid":"3881d473788c0c09ddae942e19aa0227e58a3ab7","tid":1997605,"uid":54051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t8TXG7Wpq1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft8TXG7Wpq1M&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14pVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=84bc3ab3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t8TXG7Wpq1M</a>"},{"pid":"dca231889edb5d4610a54cf4156fe5ed809c0330","tid":1997605,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"市場細 成本高 受眾少"},{"pid":"429b5459fbd6116a50acb21dcd69a3ee079649be","tid":1997605,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:12:48.000Z","msg":"唔覺得市場細係最關鍵 以前啲人一樣係咁